In the game Endless Space 2 you will find an exciting role of the leader of civilization, making the first steps in the cold depths of interstellar space. You will explore mysterious star systems, discover the secrets of ancient races, develop advanced technologies of unthinkable power, and, of course, meet new forms of life, seeking mutual understanding, the opportunity to conquer and conquer. Your story unfolds in a galaxy first colonized by a people known as the Infinite, whose sunrise and sunset was eternity ago. All that remained of them are mysterious ruins, powerful artifacts and an unusual, almost magical substance, known as Dust.
